Subject: Policy Creation
Description:
I am facing an issue with creating a policy creation especially when assigning it to a specific group - I get this prompt "Currently the system is using both computer and user rights, computer rights have priority.". 
Can one of you assist me with this request ? Happy to connect on a call to walk you through it.
Solution_Comment__c:
